                  issue: 'String concatenation with + inside a loop',
                  context: 'for token in tokens: result += token builds a new string object every iteration — O(n²) time. For a 10,000-token NLP preprocessing loop this is measurably slow.',
                  fix: 'Collect into a list and join once: " ".join(tokens). join() makes a single allocation and one pass — the standard Python pattern for building strings from parts.',
                },
